I can’t believe it’s finally here! Well, we were still installing bathroom cabinetry an hour after the party started, but hey, all’s well that ends well, right?! 
I am so excited to finally share our private house showroom @unacasaprivada with you all. I feel like I’ve been in self imposed lock down for the last year and a half and can’t wait to reconnect 🧘‍♀️ 
Thank you to everyone involved… “it takes a village” doesn’t even begin to describe it. A vision is nothing without the incredible teams bringing it to life 🙏🏼
We’ll be sharing lots more soon, but enjoy a glimpse of a wonderful evening and thank you to everyone who turned up and made it all worth this incredible journey! 🤍
